Category:  OLC  Topic:  stat_script



This function allows you to list a single script in it's entirety.  The
client will be able to recognize this and have a menu specially designed to
help you edit the script.

usage:  stat_script [mob_num] <i_th trigger> [trigger_name]

Example:
	stat_script 50 say                  // view the first say script
	stat_script 50 3.say                // view the third say script



See Also:  list_scripts add_mob_script rm_script
